      "content": "it's just so much, u know? like i was looking at photos of deep space last night and it just hit me. everything we do, every single thing... it's just a tiny blip in a void that doesn't even care we're here. in a billion years none of this will have happened. it feels like such a cruel joke to have to struggle and feel all this pain just for it to mean absolutely nothing in the end.",
